snippet.title: Age of Wonders III Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Age of Wonders III is the return of the legendary fantasy series and offers a unique mix of Empire Building, Role Playing and Warfare. This trailer shows the game's 6 leader classes in action and a sample of the many forces opposing them. For more information visit us at http://ageofwonders.com.
